Package it.polimi.deib.se2019.sanp4.adrenaline.model.match

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CardStack<T>
    A generic interface representing a stack of cards that can be drawn and discarded
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoShufflingStack<T>
    A generic class implementing the CardStack interface.
    Leaderboard
    Holds an overview of the information about scores and other metric at the end of the match.
    Leaderboard.Entry
    Holds information about final score, performed killshots, performed overkills and number of deaths for a single player.
    Match
    Hold the representation of the match.
    MatchConfiguration
    Represent the configuration needed to create a new match.
    MatchCreator
    Helper static class used by ModelImpl to create a new Match This class uses BoardCreator ActionCardCreator AmmoCardCreator PowerupCreator WeaponCreator Using the methods in this class without loading JSON resources in these creators first might lead to unexpected behavior (e.g. empty card stacks)
    PlayerTurn
    A representation of the turn of a player It contains information about: The current action performed by the player The number of actions available for the player to perform The player the turn belongs to The list of all the players damaged during the turn
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PlayerOperationEnum
    Represents the operation that a player can perform during his turn
    PlayerTurnState
    Identifies the state of a turn
